{
  "texts": [
    "The framework maintains separate evaluation criteria for financial classification, numerical reasoning, and text generation tasks.",
    "Evaluation.",
    "Performance measurement occurs through task-specific metrics, including accuracy, F1 scores, precision, recall, and BLEU scores for generation tasks.",
    "These metrics are computed using standardized implementations to ensure consistency across evaluations.",
    "FLAME aggregates results by grouping scores according to task categories and financial domains."
  ]
}